{"tid":1392592,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「活色生香」可唔可以用condom掉狗","createTime":"2019-07-31T20:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T22:14:56.000Z","uid":36481,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a33b1f022d4729b672da9a70bd63e9a85165c2","tid":1392592,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:06:54.000Z","msg":"香城online啲狗狗好鍾意玩遊戲<br />\n水彈啊、漆彈啊、不知名液體彈<br />\n製作內容其實我唔清楚<br />\n但大概都係揾個容器入住啲液體姐<br />\n可唔可以試下用condom呢<br />\n<br />\n1. 辱狗，等啲狗狗知道佢地係condom，心理擊潰<br />\n比人掉到成身condom, 狗仔狗乸個內心實覺得好羞恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 買活色生香，撐下本地真黃色品牌，雖然佢cut tvb廣告但平時唔夠膽用佢<br />\n<br />\n3. 提升士氣！ Remind返「香港警察除左黑暗醜惡，仲好撚蠢架...紙皮都得，咁condom都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n利申：講緊係香城online 玩寵物系統"},{"pid":"7421e5ad056639df18a05c37981bce6b61967f30","tid":1392592,"uid":211989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:38:02.000Z","msg":"Just do it"},{"pid":"80784bf8d5605c72da4cb592cfb848a42a6db193","tid":1392592,"uid":36481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:40:09.000Z","msg":"有2隻狗狗負評<br />\n係咪好驚比人射到成身都係姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b774cd9397ad604b2278bab226d16360e9033af","tid":1392592,"uid":142433,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:43:24.000Z","msg":"太易穿 會teamkill"},{"pid":"ef02b87cccf694089b0c071b8699bd01da935ad5","tid":1392592,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b774cd9397ad604b2278bab226d16360e9033af","tid":1392592,"uid":142433,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:43:24.000Z","msg":"太易穿 會teamkill"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:44:37.000Z","msg":"我仲心諗實好防漏添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\